author_ssm: Processed by Anna Helgeson (2007), with additions by Catherine Newton (2012) and Joseph Ditta (2019).
abstract_ssm: This collection includes member and meeting information of the women's writing group, Causeries du Lundi, founded in 1880 and still active today. Members of this group write and present their essays at meetings, gathering the first Monday of every month in the winter.
